{"tid":2102963,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[抒情,唔係感情煩惱] 學校提早暑假 令我無得再係118遇到你","createTime":"2020-07-11T01:17:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T23:25:47.000Z","uid":361232,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8c26e6c7f2b7453f1df95315ddc0e15b59a796f5","tid":2102963,"uid":361232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T01:17:24.000Z","msg":"希望大家可以幫我輕輕推一推post <br />\n小弟萬分感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"violet\">只要每日見到你一面 就已經足夠</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我住新界   要過海返工   每日都要5點幾起身 <br />\n同之前8點起身都唔會遲到相比   真係好唔慣<br />\n好記得第一日返工搭車個陣   真係眼都打唔開<br />\n直至去到紅磡轉118巴士個陣<br />\n<span class=\"violet\">我見到你</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個著住校服既女仔<br />\n紮住高馬尾   有對水汪汪既眼睛<br />\n揹住一個粉紫色fjallraven kanken背囊<br />\n背囊上面有隻黃色哈哈笑既襟章同掛住隻粉紅色既公仔<br />\n你感覺呆下呆下咁   真係可愛到唔識去形容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n望住你   我當堂成個人醒哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後每日返工都會唔覺意咁留意你<br />\n之後知道左你會搭111巴士   通常7點3左右係紅磡轉車<br />\n然後我每日都會計好時間   希望可以同你搭同一班118<br />\n有陣會以為你搭遲左一班車而選擇繼續等 <br />\n跟住搞到自己遲到<br />\n有時會因為塞車搞到遲左   撞你唔到   跟住我全日都會變到好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能個天知道今日會係我最後一次可以見你   <br />\n而之後就要等到9月開學<br />\n所以好幸運地比左個機會我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本來可以坐係你隔離<br />\n但好可惜有個男人快我一步坐左係你隔離。。。<br />\n明明附近有好多位    而偏偏佢係都要坐個度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"violet\">我知道你有睇連登<br />\n我只係想講   希望你呢個暑假過得開心平安 <br />\n等9月可以再見返你   咁樣就已經好足夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><span class=\"green\">如果你睇到呢個post,又知道我係邊個既話，希望你可以add我tg: SeeYouEveryday</span></span>"},{"pid":"7953bf7aa9f38174460d2f5d86b6e3d4a25737bf","tid":2102963,"uid":276658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T01:24:32.000Z","msg":"學生不應談戀愛"},{"pid":"e87bc9e2ff0bc908c5cad7c7adae61fa28e08cd6","tid":2102963,"uid":56550,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T01:34:50.000Z","msg":"變態stalker<br />\n死開一邊打飛機啦"},{"pid":"62c1ce9196ec76aa4ea056e7097e7950aeb48d64","tid":2102963,"uid":361232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7953bf7aa9f38174460d2f5d86b6e3d4a25737bf","tid":2102963,"uid":276658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T01:24:32.000Z","msg":"學生不應談戀愛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T01:44:17.000Z","msg":"唔係想追佢 其實只係想拎佢ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ffaca240fb39924e7fbdff81290ae5740573de","tid":2102963,"uid":361232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e87bc9e2ff0bc908c5cad7c7adae61fa28e08cd6","tid":2102963,"uid":56550,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T01:34:50.000Z","msg":"變態stalker<br />\n死開一邊打飛機啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T01:45:04.000Z","msg":"唔係變態 慢慢成為左精神上既寄托<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d889330ee8dc8eab3725b7937e2afc08ed6d9e2d","tid":2102963,"uid":361232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202